{"tid":578183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐陽耀冲回流！ 自由身加盟港超夢想FC","createTime":"2018-03-02T11:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T11:55:35.000Z","uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"e2659ada9f35795defc27152f530fe7516552720","tid":578183,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"經過四年外流生涯，歐陽耀冲正式回流香港，與夢想FC簽下合約，將會穿上89號球衣。<br />\n<br />\n「歐冲」於2014年毅然離開香港，去到歐洲力爭外流機會，結果成功加盟葡甲的葡萄牙體育會，其後曾效力洛里什，至2016年轉投當時在中甲的貴州恒豐。不過，昨日貴州宣佈與港腳法圖斯續約後，已用上該隊的「港澳台內援」名額，而歐冲亦沒有出現在新球季中超球員名單中，他本人近日亦正隨夢想操練。結果夢想今日黃昏宣佈，與歐陽耀冲簽約，後者將會穿上89號球衣。"},{"pid":"7bf43404e55d1c382d9d6d94e08a1d8e1ab9b2da","tid":578183,"uid":12034,"like":109,"dislike":3,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"夢想已完"},{"pid":"2adb7c0936975cc342dbbc6d8b4f2bdac8eb6249","tid":578183,"uid":9030,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"雖歐冲錯過港超轉會窗, 但消息指他仍可以以失業球員身份註冊, 下半季為夢想FC出戰"},{"pid":"21beddccf2fae0a4052c6d6ed64c3892318afeaa","tid":578183,"uid":36497,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"幾乎忘記了呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3b9ae4fd60a84222677d97cfac668919c6d8f7","tid":578183,"uid":23833,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"根本目的已逹成<br />\n<br />\n出外國做後備狗<br />\n<br />\n浸一浸咸水<br />\n<br />\n返到香港已經可以做球皇"},{"pid":"60564344d305182924c4e0d881604e2e01ba4baa","tid":578183,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"76939e3e9f721b4a411c9bbab8ddf2dcbda9927c","tid":578183,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c373881fb3f99dfa7802c41bfb9cdaac515f6abe","tid":578183,"uid":44580,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"外流4年定外遊4年？"},{"pid":"ed79cc3a1c3fafc6ed629e1be5db5c844336bb12","tid":578183,"uid":37732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dreamsfcofficial/videos/173528819943067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdreamsfcofficial%2Fvideos%2F173528819943067%2F&d=9PSWKmoeL2jtaxRuB1Z%2BeZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ea81cccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dreamsfcofficial/videos/173528819943067/</a>"},{"pid":"13fa535d40575374d1542d9cb5998a6a47aa1b89","tid":578183,"uid":9030,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"總結歐陽耀冲四年外流生涯，佢先加盟葡甲球會葡萄牙體育會，一年間出場55分鐘，顧及上陣機會，效力葡萄牙體育會翌季季初選擇外借去葡乙球會洛里什，出場5次。兩個月後，歐陽耀冲以內援身份加盟中甲貴州智誠簽約三年，第一及兩年共為一隊上陣121分鐘，到第三年開季前的三天，歐陽耀冲在社交網站貼上「#中超 #又一年」的體驗照片，惜兩日後因同隊港澳台球員法圖斯被介定為港澳台球員，獲得續約，而條例所限一隊一港澳台球員，歐陽耀冲須離隊，而轉會窗關閉前難以找其他中國球會落班，歐陽耀冲無奈選擇回流港超加盟夢想FC。"},{"pid":"035e29eff390bdbc2bf3adfc0954a82f5c93469c","tid":578183,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed79cc3a1c3fafc6ed629e1be5db5c844336bb12","tid":578183,"uid":37732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dreamsfcofficial/videos/173528819943067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdreamsfcofficial%2Fvideos%2F173528819943067%2F&d=9PSWKmoeL2jtaxRuB1Z%2BeZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ea81cccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dreamsfcofficial/videos/173528819943067/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"hi admin"},{"pid":"408178452cac6c9b733fd18b3179477d27747f9f","tid":578183,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"做乜咁多負評.........."},{"pid":"e4048c27b3a9c88b20bd24d8ebddc038cad18f58","tid":578183,"uid":63017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夢想已完</blockq